                                        <p>Side note - just for example</p>
                                    </authorialNote>
                                    The Constitution of Bungeni is amended in<ref id="ref3"
                                                                                  href="/ak/act/2010-08-27/1/main#sect47A">
                                    section 47A</ref>—
                                </listIntroduction>
                                <item id="sec2-lst1-itma">
                                    <p>
                                        (a) in<ref id="ref4" href="/ak/act/2010-08-27/1/main#sec47A-sub2-itmb">
