                                                a majority</quotedText>”;
                                        </mod>
                                    </p>
                                </item>
                                <item id="sec2-lst1-itmb">
                                    <p>(b) by inserting the following new subsection immediately after
                                        <ref id="ref5" href="/ak/act/2010-08-27/1/main#sec47A-sub3">subsection (3)</ref>
                                        —
                                        <mod id="sec2-lst1-itmb-mod1">“
                                            <quotedStructure id="sec2-lst1-itmb-mod1-qtd1">
